  {
    num: '04',
    title: 'Dedicated Contract Carriage',
    desc: 'Dedicated fleet capacity for shippers with predictable volume — fixed rates, guaranteed equipment, and service-level commitments that hold up under pressure.',
  },
  {
    num: '05',
    title: 'Expedited + Time-Critical',
    desc: 'Team-driver and expedited options for aerospace, defense, and manufacturing shipments that can\'t wait for a standard transit window.',
  },
  {
    num: '06',
    title: 'Brokerage + Capacity Sourcing',
    desc: 'Vetted carrier network across the Southeast and Midwest — with rate transparency and load tracking so you always know what you\'re paying for.',
